This is the code I used to connect An Arduino (MEGA-2560) to Unity Engine.
arduino version 1.8.12
Unity 2019.3.12
Uduino 3.1

arduino mega 2560
sparkfun lsm9ds1 breakout
elegoo joystick

libraries:
    Arduino:
        sparkfunlsm9ds1.h
        uduino.h
        wire.h
        
    C# || monodevelop:
        using System.Collections;
        using System.Collections.Generic;
        using UnityEngine;
        using Uduino;
        using System;
